{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/datalad/datalad/issues/5941", "id": 983702409, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU5ODM3MDI0MDk=", "number": 5941, "title": "`create-sibling-github --existing skip` configures a sibling", "user": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 390153891, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwzOTAxNTM4OTE=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/labels/UX", "name": "UX", "color": "0052cc", "default": false, "description": "user experience"}, {"id": 2803374957, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyODAzMzc0OTU3", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/labels/cmd-create-sibling-github", "name": "cmd-create-sibling-github", "color": "FEF2C0", "default": false, "description": ""}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2021-08-31T10:30:54Z", "updated_at": "2021-09-22T17:47:28Z", "closed_at": "2021-09-22T17:47:28Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Not sure how I feel about this behavior. I have a dataset that I want to create a github sibling for. I (accidentally) chose a repo name that conflicts with an already existing repo on github. So this behavior is good:\r\n\r\n```\r\n% datalad create-sibling-github funkydummy3\r\ncreate_sibling_github(error): . (dataset) [repository \"funkydummy3\" already exists on Github]\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut this one, I cannot easily get behind:\r\n\r\n```\r\n% datalad create-sibling-github funkydummy3 --existing skip\r\nconfigure-sibling(ok): . (sibling)\r\naction summary:\r\n  configure-sibling (ok: 1)\r\n  create_sibling_github (notneeded: 1)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI does skip the creation of the repo (to avoid the conflict), but it also proceeds to configure the (totally unrelated repo, in my case) as a sibling.\r\n\r\nI would have expected the `existing='skip'` to mean \"if there already is a sibling configured, skip\", not \"if there already is a repo, skip creation, but configure a sibling\".\r\n\r\nI think I would expect such a behavior with `existing='reconfigure'`, but not with `skip`.", "closed_by": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5941/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}